//  the arms are tried in order; the first whose pattern matches wins; and
//  pattern variables BIND per arm (a bare name matches anything, catch-all
//  style). If nothing matches, the whole case FAILS — failure being an ordinary
//  outcome here, not an error.
//
//  WORKED EXAMPLE:
//
//      case 2 {
//        1 => "one";
//        2 => "two";
//        x => ["other", x]     // x binds to the scrutinee
